58
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:48,590
I'm sorry.

59
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:49,910
It's okay.

60
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,560
Jiaxu,

61
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:56,750
