62
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:57,560
The New Year's Eve?

63
00:02:57,960 --> 00:03:01,190
I'll watch the Spring Festival Gala.

64
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:01,960
Then...

65
00:03:02,910 --> 00:03:04,680
I'll wait for your New Year message.

66
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,400
That's all?

67
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,190
Yeah.

68
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:07,710
Oh.

69
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,560
I'll go back to Nanwu after the New Year

70
