How about

76
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,590
you get me a girlfriend?

77
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:25,080
Me?

78
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:26,680
But the girls I know

79
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,560
are almost of my age.

80
00:03:31,960 --> 00:03:33,360
Of your age?

81
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,800
Mm.

82
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:38,520
I'm okay with that.

83
00:03:40,590 --> 00:03:41,520
What did you say?

84
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:44,720
[Yihe University]

85
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:53,960
Don't break in. Swipe your card.

86
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:56,400
Don't break in. Swipe your card.

87
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:57,150
Jiaxu.

88
