Drink slowly.

91
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,190
I have something to ask you.

92
00:04:24,310 --> 00:04:25,390
Will you ask me

93
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:27,310
about the bar thing last night?

94
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:29,070
I went there with my roommates.

95
00:04:29,070 --> 00:04:30,560
I hadn't been there before.

96
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,390
Are you sure?

97
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:34,070
But why did I hear a boy's voice

98
00:04:34,070 --> 00:04:35,750
on the phone last night?

99
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,390
It sounded quite familiar.

100
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:42,160
"Sang Zhi, I saw a cat
outside your dorm."

101
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:45,190
So, is he Mr. Charming?

102
00:04:45,190 --> 00:04:45,920
No.

103
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:48,510
Then, is your Mr. Charming

104
00:04:49,510 --> 00:04:51,070
quite girlish?

105
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:53,510
No.

106
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,190
He's manly.

107
00:04:57,870 --> 00:05:00,190
So, you like muscly fellows.

108
00:05:00,310 --> 00:05:00,630
Huh?

109
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,870
Don't be so gossipy, okay?

110
00:05:02,950 --> 00:05:05,190
You're the biggest gossiper
I've ever seen.

111
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,480
You know,

112
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,120
