113
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,870
But you're right, anyway.

114
00:05:10,070 --> 00:05:11,720
I'm indeed gossipy.

115
00:05:11,870 --> 00:05:13,800
Then, tell me more

116
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,950
