117
00:05:22,750 --> 00:05:24,310
What? Do you also want some?

118
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,750
Ah.

119
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,430
Want me to feed you?

120
00:05:27,750 --> 00:05:28,240
Mm.

121
00:05:28,390 --> 00:05:29,800
Can't you eat it yourself?

122
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,800
My hands are dirty
on the steering wheel.

123
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,680
Zhi.

124
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:41,800
What's up?

125
00:05:42,190 --> 00:05:43,240
Be careful with your hands.

126
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,750
Don't flirt with me.

127
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:49,430
Ah.

128
00:05:49,430 --> 00:05:50,160
No more.

129
00:05:58,070 --> 00:06:00,360
Last night, did I tell him anything

130
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,950
I shouldn't have said?

131
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,480
No way.

132
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:06,000
If I had really thrown up on him,

133
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,310
how could he

134
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,800
