135
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,560
He must have lost his mind.

136
00:06:19,270 --> 00:06:20,070
Sang Yan.

137
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:22,920
How disrespectful!

138
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,800
You told me not to call you brother.

139
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,270
I also told you

140
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:27,600
