141
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:28,600
Did you listen?

142
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,950
You told me you would skimp.

143
00:06:32,190 --> 00:06:33,600
Have you weighed yourself lately?

144
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,600
You...

145
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,950
