147
00:06:39,430 --> 00:06:40,510
Mom.

148
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:41,830
Oh, Zhizhi.

149
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,310
Mom, I'm back.

150
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:44,750
Oh, my honey.

151
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,830
