164
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:13,600
You're no longer young.

165
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,070
But you don't have a girlfriend.

166
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:17,360
When can I have a grandson?

167
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:18,920
You always piss me off.

168
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:22,390
Come on. Take a rest.

169
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:23,480
Lunch will be ready.

170
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,000
Oh.

171
00:07:24,310 --> 00:07:24,600
Mm.

172
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,310
Yan,

173
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,830
