183
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,120
You'll have a blind date together.

184
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,920
Shut up, okay?

185
00:07:58,480 --> 00:07:59,190
Forget it, then.

186
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:00,680
Whatever you do.

187
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,680
You...

188
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,360
