189
00:08:14,630 --> 00:08:16,000
Who are you talking to?

190
00:08:16,070 --> 00:08:17,240
You look so happy.

191
00:08:17,950 --> 00:08:19,430
Kid, you know what?

192
00:08:19,750 --> 00:08:21,950
