204
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:35,310
♪If we meet again, don't hug me♪

205
00:09:35,370 --> 00:09:38,410
♪I don't want it this way♪

206
00:09:38,410 --> 00:09:42,030
♪I can't see or force a smile♪

207
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:45,510
♪I'll just forget it♪

208
00:09:45,770 --> 00:09:49,710
♪If I can't cover
the corners of my eyes♪

